records.addlTxt:
Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three (3) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) Pay restitution of $6,419.37 to Kip Derosier and Raise Rite Concrete at a rate to be determined by the agent;
2) Defendant is to have no contact with Kip Derosier or Raise Rite Concrete;
3) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
4) Maintain fulltime employment, work search or combination;
5) AODA assessment and follow through;
6) Spend four (4) months in the county jail, under the Huber Law/child care, on count 2 only, commencing on 10-19-18 by 5:00 p.m.;
7) Pay court costs;
8) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Minutes.
